= SDL_GetTextureBlendMode =
Use this function to get the blend mode used for texture copy operations.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetTextureBlendMode(SDL_Texture* texture,
                            int*         blendMode)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''texture'''
|the texture to query
|-
|'''blendMode'''
|a pointer filled in with the current [[SDL_BlendMode]]
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or -1 if the texture is not valid; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

